e","url":"https://www.isasecure.org","description":"ISASecure provides certification guidelines emphasizing traceability in ICS security."}]},{"id":"KA2","title":"Peer Review Processes","description":"Peer reviews involve cross-functional teams validating security implementations against design requirements. This reduces human error and ensures alignment with security capabilities.","related_links":[{"title":"Honeywell ICS Peer Review Framework","url":" https://www.honeywellprocess.com/library/support/technical-documents/cybersecurity-best-practices.pdf","description":"Honeywell's framework for conducting peer reviews in ICS environments."},{"title":"NIST SP 800-82 Rev. 3","url":"https://csrc.nist.gov/publications/detail/sp/800-82/rev-3/final","description":"NIST guidelines on ICS security, including peer review best practices."}]},{"id":"KA3","title":"Automated Security Checks","description":"Automated tools scan implementations for deviations from security designs. This is essential for large-scale ICS deployments where manual reviews are impractical.","related_links":[{"title":"Schneider Electric EcoStruxure Security","url":"https://www.se.com/ww/en/work/solutions/cybersecurity/","description":"Schneider's tools for automated security checks in ICS."},{"title":"Rockwell Automation Security Solutions","url":"https://www.rockwellautomation.com/en-us/products/security.html","description":"Rockwell's solutions for automating ICS security compliance checks."}]},{"id":"KA4","title":"Deviation Documentation","description":"Documenting deviations with risk assessments ensures transparency and justifies alternative security measures. This aligns with IEC 62443-4-1's risk-based approach.","related_links":[{"title":"ISA IEC 62443 Risk Assessment Guide","url":" https://www.isa.org/standards-and-publications/isa-standards/isa-iec-62443-series-of-standards","description":"ISA's guide on risk assessments for ICS security deviations."},{"title":"CISA ICS Risk Management","url":"